title: Hour 3 - Tua "Back" Injury Questions, Manningcast Involved in Pro Bowl?
itunes:title: Hour 3 - Tua "Back" Injury Questions, Manningcast Involved in Pro Bowl?
description:
Dan questions the handling of Miami Dolphins QB Tua Tagovailoa's injury which looked more like a concussion than the back injury it is being reported as. And he discusses the possibility of Peyton Manning getting involved in broadcasting the Pro Bowl next year.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
